reviews.review_text: Superior Sound This new upload is by FAR the best offering of this excellent show. If there’s a better sounding soundboard recording on this site I’d sure like to know about it. 5 stars in all categories by any reasonable standard. The China->Rider with its joyfully executed feeling groovy jam shouldn’t be missed (nor the post Truckin’ jam that births Let It Grow) but honestly I suspect you’ll find yourself pleased wherever you land in this must have performance by the dead - Peaking with ideas and energy - Executing with face melting ferocity.
